      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "For supervised analysis, besides limma-based DMP and ProbeLasso-based DMR analysis functions (Butcher and Beck, 2015), there is now added functionality for DMR detection using Bumphunter (Jaffe et al., 2012) and DMRcate (Peters et al., 2015).",
