    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/dmr-detection-bumphunter/008",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Large-scale differentially methylated blocks (DMB) can also be identified. These DMBs are large-scale genomic regions (10 kb\u2013Mb) containing hundreds of inter-genic CpG sites",
      "asbval:note": "Paper describes DMBs (large-scale blocks with hundreds of CpGs) but does not specify minimum CpG threshold (\u22653) for bumphunter-based DMR detection. The \u22653 CpG threshold is a standard bumphunter parameter not explicitly stated in the paper.",
