      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The new version of ChAMP, extends and improves this analysis pipeline, adding novel and enhanced functionalities, including detection of differentially methylated genomic blocks (DMB), gene set enrichment analysis (GSEA), a method for correcting cell-type heterogeneity and detection of differentially methylated gene modules.",
