      "asbval:evidence_quote": "ChAMP loads data from IDAT files using it's novel loading function, or though minfi loading function (Aryee et al., 2014). Probes can be filtered based on detection P-values, chromosomal location, presence of single nucleotide polymorphisms in the probe sequence (Zhou et al., 2016) and cross-hybridization.",
